billEvents.eventText: REFERRED TO INVESTIGATIONS AND GOVERNMENT OPERATIONS

title: Allows taxpayers to contribute to the support of the animal population control fund by marking a space on a corporate or personal income tax return
summary: Allows taxpayers to contribute to the support of the animal population control fund by marking a space on a corporate or personal income tax return.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the tax law, in relation to contributions to the animal population control fund
